.RE
.sp
\fBRUBY_CONFIGURE_OPTS\fP
.RS 4
Additional "./configure" arguments that apply only to Ruby source
.RE
.sp
\fBRUBY_MAKE_OPTS\fP
.RS 4
Additional make arguments that apply only to Ruby source
.RE
.sp
\fBRUBY_MAKE_INSTALL_OPTS\fP
